{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259243, "create_time": 1656313818, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "黑可以，不要乱黑好不好，不知道什么叫逆城市化吧", "timestamp": 1656313818}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259246, "create_time": 1656313929, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "尬住", "timestamp": 1656313929}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259257, "create_time": 1656314127, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 正常的逆城市化是人们用脚投票，自愿离开大城市。中国的减量发展，是人们想进大城市、留在大城市，政府设置门槛不让进，甚至把人们赶走。", "timestamp": 1656314127}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259261, "create_time": 1656314185, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 就非得要病入膏肓了才能治病是吧？治未病不行吗？", "timestamp": 1656314185}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259272, "create_time": 1656314393, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 可以可以，让我猜猜，你是不是也认为动态清零是治未病？比共存高明多了？是药三分毒，没病吃药，会有副作用的哦", "timestamp": 1656314393}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259275, "create_time": 1656314433, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Carol: 可是如果不控制的话，大城市和其他地区的差异不就越来越大吗？", "timestamp": 1656314433}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259277, "create_time": 1656314469, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 那等着病到快死掉再吃药，在毁灭中发展吧，也不是不可以", "timestamp": 1656314469}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259279, "create_time": 1656314534, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 北京的大城市病还不够明显吗？\n", "timestamp": 1656314534}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259281, "create_time": 1656314601, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 就搞成里约，新德里那样贫民窟成片，富人区流油了再谈城市治理？你觉得你会在富人区还是在贫民窟里面？", "timestamp": 1656314601}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259285, "create_time": 1656314766, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 现实是，外来务工人员宁可住棚户区，也不愿被当做低端人口清理出去", "timestamp": 1656314766}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259287, "create_time": 1656314819, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 你觉得你会成为能享受到减量发展成果的北京市民，还是成为被清理出去的低端人口？", "timestamp": 1656314819}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259288, "create_time": 1656314853, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 那是，贫民窟的百万贫民也宁愿住在贫民窟里啊", "timestamp": 1656314853}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259293, "create_time": 1656314944, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 多说也没啥意义，人都是屁股决定脑袋，让我猜猜，Alice是不是北京人？已经拿到北京户口了？认为自己是人上人？外地低端人口早就该全赶走？", "timestamp": 1656314944}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259301, "create_time": 1656315136, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 如果你认同减量发展，请你扪心自问，你自己是否愿意卖掉西城区的学区房搬到通州去？你是否愿意注销北京户口，搬到雄安新区去？", "timestamp": 1656315136}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259305, "create_time": 1656315374, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "没关系，支持，反正被轰走的不会是我。小知识：北京外来务工人员远多于本地户口居民", "timestamp": 1656315374}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259342, "create_time": 1656316753, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Alice 应该不知道人口的自由迁徙在大多数国家都是受到宪法保障的吧。", "timestamp": 1656316753}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259348, "create_time": 1656316831, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "或者 Alice 认为外地人生来就是比北京老爷低一等、不配待在发展水平更好的地方。", "timestamp": 1656316831}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259358, "create_time": 1656317050, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 整体的差异会扩大，但因为人口流向了大城市，人均享有的资源数量反而会趋同。", "timestamp": 1656317050}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259360, "create_time": 1656317213, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Francis: 我来给你补充一下，中国宪法也曾经写过“迁徙自由”，后来删了。联合国《公民权利和政治权利国际公约》也规定了迁徙自由，中国签署可这个公约，但全国人大迄今没有批准这个公约，所以在中国国内没有效力。", "timestamp": 1656317213}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259363, "create_time": 1656317338, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Francis: 可是更多的人口流向大城市，特别是青年和人才，使得大城市发展的越来越好", "timestamp": 1656317338}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259365, "create_time": 1656317384, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Francis: 另一方面，其他地区的人口在流失，原本就没什么产业，结果现在更不会有产业愿意去了", "timestamp": 1656317384}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259368, "create_time": 1656317467, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Francis: 自由流动的一个负面影响是，会导致强的更强，弱的更弱。这样是不是在加剧不同地区之间发展的不平衡呢？", "timestamp": 1656317467}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259371, "create_time": 1656317585, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 大城市的地理气候环境决定了更适合经济发展人类生存啊。人更多的迁徙到适合生存的地方，对整个社会不好吗？", "timestamp": 1656317585}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259375, "create_time": 1656317800, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Francis: 如果这么看的话，那东部地区的自然条件确实比中西部地区有利", "timestamp": 1656317800}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259384, "create_time": 1656317994, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Francis: 那是应该采取一些措施去缓解中西部地区与东部地区发展的差异？还是应该尊重中西部地区与东部地区的这种差异呢？", "timestamp": 1656317994}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259388, "create_time": 1656318074, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 对整个国家来说，把人口更多地迁移到东部，总产出肯定会提升。那把增加的部分产出财政转移给中西部，中西部留下的人也能过得更舒服。", "timestamp": 1656318074}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259392, "create_time": 1656318187, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 利益受损的只是发达地区的原住民了，因为人口迁入导致他们原来独占的资源在短期内被稀释掉了。", "timestamp": 1656318187}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259401, "create_time": 1656318396, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Francis: 这种转移，足以弥补让他们过的更舒服吗？", "timestamp": 1656318396}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259402, "create_time": 1656318403, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Francis: 当然，这是在世界和平的假定下。如果世界不太平，那还是不要把所有鸡蛋放在一个篮子里为妙，这就和三线建设是一个道理。风险和效率，总得取舍一下。", "timestamp": 1656318403}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259405, "create_time": 1656318490, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Francis: 比如以北京和河北为例，北京的人才和产业越来越多，河北的人才和产业越来越小。（因为大家用脚投票，都想去北京，很少有人会想去河北）", "timestamp": 1656318490}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259407, "create_time": 1656318548, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 除了转移之外，中西部本身的人均资源也扩大了。你原来一家只有两亩地；城市化导致一半农民迁去东部沿海了，你家就有四亩地了，可以搞机械化生产了，挣的钱从期望上看应该更多了。", "timestamp": 1656318548}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259408, "create_time": 1656318589, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Dave: 那北京需要转移多少给河北才合适呢？", "timestamp": 1656318589}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259413, "create_time": 1656318629, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 人才和产业，就是要集中起来才有更高的生产率。这就是城市存在的原因。", "timestamp": 1656318629}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259414, "create_time": 1656318648, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "笑死，之前广东说腾笼换鸟，结果直接把鸟换到东南亚去了", "timestamp": 1656318648}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259417, "create_time": 1656318685, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Francis: 比如教育资源，医疗资源，也都是很重要的资源，这些人均资源一定会因此扩大吗？", "timestamp": 1656318685}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259419, "create_time": 1656318760, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 转移多少就不是我考虑得到的了，我就一键盘侠哪懂什么财政。", "timestamp": 1656318760}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259423, "create_time": 1656318847, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Dave: 像是耕地，总人口少了，确实人均土地就多了。但是医生老师，总人口少了，可是优秀的医生可能也相应的流失了，所以人均医疗和教育资源可能反而会下降。", "timestamp": 1656318847}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259425, "create_time": 1656318902, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 腾笼换鸟一方面是因为劳动力成本太高了，比不了东南亚。那开放户籍，让落后地区的劳动力迁移过来，劳动力充沛了，劳动力成本就可以压下去。", "timestamp": 1656318902}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 259431, "create_time": 1656319178, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 你这分子分母都减小了，咋知道比值到底是下降还是上升了呢。但总体上看，人均资源更多了，各类具体的资源（教育、医疗）应该趋向于提升，而不是下降。", "timestamp": 1656319178}], "create_time": 1656313658, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1656319178, "likenum": 6, "n_attentions": 6, "n_comments": 39, "pid": 73674, "poll": null, "reply": 39, "text": "不以为耻，反以为荣\n![](https://gateway.pinata.cloud/ipfs/bafybeihdqc4x2ltffrd2bfeiru7aihowquofpooab72zrhfj3yc75avqsi?filename=49329D44-162A-4C77-AE8E-52E15B720240.jpeg&filetype=image%2Fjpeg) [加载失败请点击此](https://hole.thu.monster/ipfs.html#bafybeihdqc4x2ltffrd2bfeiru7aihowquofpooab72zrhfj3yc75avqsi)\n\n---\n", "timestamp": 1656313658}}